description: Disables root user sessions for privileged tasks across member accounts in your organization. When you disable this feature, the management account and the delegated administrator for IAM can no longer perform privileged tasks on member accounts in your organization.

nested_items.description: The features you have enabled for centralized root access of member accounts in your organization.
